"{\"uid\": \"timesnownews.com-world-olympic-village-inn-palisades-shooting-reports-police-investigating-incident-amid-shooting-reports-article-107175296\", \"text\": \"World  Placer County Sheriff revealed limited details about the incident on a social media post on X.  There has been a critical incident at the Olympic Village Inn at Palisades, according to the Placer County Sheriff's office.  Placer County Sheriff revealed limited details about the incident on a social media post on X.  The sheriff's office released a statement on social media just after 11 a.m. on Friday, Jan. 26 stating the incident is stable but there is a large police presence as a result.  \\\"There was a critical incident that occurred at Olympic Village Inn at Palisades. State Parks was the primary agency for the incident. The incident is stable, but there is still a large police presence. Please stay clear of the area,\\\" the Sheriff's post read.    The Sheriff's Office has provided an update saying that there was a shooting involving California State Park Officers,2News Nevadareported.  The Olympic Village Inn near the popular Tahoe ski resort is described as a vacation ownership hotel and resort nestled in the mountains of Olympic Valley near Lake Tahoe.  Authored by Feba Bovas  Professionals & enthusiasts who write about politics to science, from economy to education, from local issues to national events and global affairs, t...View More  Japan Earthquake, Tsunami Map: Which Regions Are Under Warning?  Japan Earthquake: 'Megaquake' Warning Issued After Massive 7.6 Quake In Northeast | What It Means  San Ramon Earthquake: Series of Tremors Hit Bay Area  Who Is David Ellison? Paramount CEO's Net Worth And Hostile Bid To Take Over Warner Bros. Discovery  Japan Earthquake Live Updates: JMA Issues 'Megaquake' Advisory; Tsunami 'Warning' Now Cancelled\"}"